Global Toilet Installation amp Repair Services Market Insights
Toilet Installation & Repair Services Market size was valued at USD 17.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 28.3 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Toilet Installation & Repair Services Market Overview
The global Toilet Installation & Repair Services Market is currently valued at approximately USD 12.5 billion in 2025 and is expected to grow significantly at a CAGR of 5.8% during the forecast period. This growth is driven by an increase in residential and commercial construction, technological advancements in plumbing systems, and a rising demand for eco-friendly sanitation solutions. With rapid urbanization, increasing disposable incomes, and the rising importance of hygiene, the market is experiencing steady expansion. Additionally, an increase in the number of service providers offering innovative and reliable toilet installation and repair solutions is propelling market growth.

